{"id": "1444650125073846373", "channel_id": "1444650125073846373", "type": 0, "author_id": "304579084766412802", "author_name": "fallen.archangel", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello. I decided to install the game on my PC and encountered the following problem:\nMorimens launches, everything works fine, I've successfully logged into my account, but when I try to enter the game, it freezes.\nIn Task Manager, the game is marked as \"Not Responding.\"\nThere are no errors in the event log.\n\nHow I tried to solve the problem:\nReinstalled the game\nInstalled from Steam (Exactly the same thing happens)\nUpdated Visual C++ and removed outdated versions\nUpdated Nvidia drivers\nUpdated Windows 10 to the latest version\nEnabled and disabled VPN and third-party internet traffic programs\n\nNote: The game works fine on my phone and laptop.", "timestamp": "2025-11-30T11:23:50.119000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-30T12:49:33.088000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1444650125485015181", "filename": "Screenshot_1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2639281, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1444650125073846373/1444650125485015181/Screenshot_1.png?ex=69ff1946&is=69fdc7c6&hm=1896f2dba6c73eaeb39c96992a918e505d7527e853a35d790222ef20ad175d73&"}, {"id": "1444650125946392697", "filename": "Screenshot_2.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 88972, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1444650125073846373/1444650125946392697/Screenshot_2.png?ex=69ff1946&is=69fdc7c6&hm=ac10bfd738111d1a225e850a8bcbd46fd49294d5ab330706709c4acd6f7dbe82&"}, {"id": "1444650126277607465", "filename": "Screenshot_21.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 21416, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1444650125073846373/1444650126277607465/Screenshot_21.png?ex=69ff1946&is=69fdc7c6&hm=798519e17d8b59589e5161c6286ada2439269fc59d7462af1711134b03c9968b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "th