{"id": "1444635935626104904", "channel_id": "1444635935626104904", "type": 0, "author_id": "527144088550768641", "author_name": "dianethedeadly", "author_bot": false, "content": "Something akin to Protoparadise but it also lets you recall Limited awakener's enlightenments with the caveat being u can only use it on an Awakener from the same arc, either Faded Legacy or Astral Reign. I know the chances of this actually being implemented are low but I'm really hoping I can somehow undo my regretful dupes at some point if this does go through~", "timestamp": "2025-11-30T10:27:27.091000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1444635935626104904", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Let us recall premium enlightenments with a small catch", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
